		<p>I feel like the challenge with the latter is to combat the notion that a commercial use is a lost licensing fee. Artists are starting to understand that a pirated download isn&#8217;t a lost sale, but still need to break from the line of thinking that they&#8217;d be missing out on all the licensing dollars they&#8217;d get if they allow commercial use. In almost all cases, they are — quite frankly — not.</p>
